tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE StockReports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date DATE,
    stock_level INT,
    sales_performance DECIMAL,
    revenue DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE SalesPerformance (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    sale_date DATE,
    quantity_sold INT,
    revenue DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
